N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 9951.1 - Statement of purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of this Part is to set forth the methods and
procedures governing the availability, location and nature of those records of
the Elderly Pharmaceutical Insurance Coverage Panel subject to the provisions
of article 6-A of the Public Officers Law, known as the Personal Privacy

Protection Law, and the rules of the Committee on Open

Government. Notes
